---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Mi Rancho — Customer Story — Formic"
  description="Mi Rancho deployed 9 robotic palletizers to support 40% annual growth — eliminating injuries and cutting downtime."
  ogTitle="Mi Rancho — Formic Customer Story"
  ogDescription="9 robotic palletizers · zero lift injuries · cut downtime"
>
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://formic.co/stories/mi-rancho" slot="head" />

<div class="detail-bc">
  <a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span><a href="/stories">Customer Stories</a><span class="sep">/</span>Mi Rancho
</div>

<section class="detail-hero">
  <div class="si">
    <div class="slabel" style="color:var(--orange)">Customer Story · Mi Rancho</div>
    <h1>40% growth,<br><em>zero new injuries.</em></h1>
    <p class="lede">Mi Rancho was growing 40% year-over-year. Manual palletizing couldn't keep up with demand, and every additional shift was an additional injury risk. Nine robotic palletizers absorbed the growth and the headcount pressure at once.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="detail-video wide">
    <div class="detail-video-frame">
      <video autoplay muted loop playsinline poster="/Talos-0095.jpg">
        <source src="/Formic-Header.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
      </video>
      <span class="dv-fpo">FPO</span>
      <span class="dv-cap">Mi Rancho · robotic palletizing</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white">
  <div class="db-grid">
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">01 — The Challenge</div>
      <h2>Growth was <em>the problem</em>.</h2>
      <p>40% annual growth strained every part of operations. Injury claims were climbing, fatigue was lengthening shifts, and the CapEx required to add fixed automation across nine lines was outside budget.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>40% YoY revenue growth, faster than headcount could keep up</li>
        <li>Climbing injury claims tied to manual palletizing</li>
        <li>Tight CapEx budget — couldn't justify nine fixed-asset purchases</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/Talos-0095.jpg" alt="Mi Rancho production cell" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">High-mix · sustained throughput</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block lgrey">
  <div class="db-grid flip">
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/Haviland_Products_-_Palletizing.gif" alt="Mi Rancho robotic palletizer" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Robotic palletizing · 9 cells</span></div>
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">02 — The Solution</div>
      <h2>Nine cells, <em>zero CapEx</em>.</h2>
      <p>Formic Full Service made nine deployments fit a CapEx-constrained budget. Each robotic palletizer runs under a fixed monthly fee — no purchase, no integration risk, no separate SLA per machine. The fleet scaled with the business.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>9 robotic palletizers across multiple lines</li>
        <li>Zero CapEx — fixed monthly Full Service agreement</li>
        <li>Single SLA across the entire fleet</li>
        <li>Capacity scaled with demand, not on a procurement cycle</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px;text-align:center">
    <div class="db-tag" style="justify-content:center">03 — The Outcome</div>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:clamp(40px,5vw,72px);font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1;color:var(--white);margin:18px 0 56px">Eliminated injuries. <em style="color:var(--orange);font-style:normal">Cut downtime.</em></h2>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.1)">
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">9</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">Robotic palletizers</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">40%</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">Annual growth absorbed</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">$0</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">CapEx</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-cta">
  <h2>Scale your floor <em>with your business.</em></h2>
  <div class="btn-row">
    <a href="mailto:sales@formic.co" class="btn-ctadark">Get Started</a>
    <a href="/stories" class="btn-ctawh">More Customer Stories</a>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
